data.description: Welcome to your new haven nestled in the heart of a tranquil suburb, where comfort meets convenience. This delightful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence is perfect for families seeking a peaceful retreat without sacrificing modern amenities. As you step inside, you're greeted by an inviting living space bathed in natural light, adorned with warm hardwood floors and tasteful decor. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the cozy living room to the gourmet kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining or family gatherings. The chef-inspired kitchen boasts sleek quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar for casual dining. Enjoy preparing meals while overlooking the lush backyard through large windows, bringing the outdoors in. Retreat to the spacious primary suite featuring a serene atmosphere and an en-suite bathroom complete with a luxurious soaking tub and separate shower. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms offer comfort and flexibility, perfect for children, guests, or a home office. Step outside to discover your private oasis, where a sprawling backyard awaits. Host summer barbecues, play with pets, or simply unwind in the shade of mature trees. The possibilities are endless in this outdoor sanctuary. Conveniently located near top-rated schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining destinations, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. With easy access to major highways, commuting to the city center is a breeze. Don't miss this opportunity to own a slice of suburban paradise. Schedule your showing today and make this charming family home yours!
